 Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cO Abu Sa\u2019id, which jihad is best?\u201d Hasan said, \u201cYour jihad against your desires.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-Muh\u0323ibbi\u0304n 1\/478 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0645 \u0648\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652 \u0642\u0650\u064a\u0644\u064e \u0644\u0650\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0635\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u0650\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0636\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062c\u0650\u0647\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064f\u0643\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26713,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/09\/jihad-greatest-enemy-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":35538,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Jihad: Your greatest enemy is your own ego","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Tabari reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYour enemy is not the one you are relieved from if you killed him. Rather, your true enemy is your own soul, between your two sides.\u201d Al-Tabari said, \u201cIt is the jihad against the greatest of enemies to a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/20\/abdullah-ibn-amr-jihad-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":35538,"position":2},"title":"Abdullah on Jihad: Start with the jihad against your soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Hannan ibn Kharija reported: I said to Abdullah ibn 'Amr, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWhat do you say about jihad and military campaigns?\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cBegin with your soul and wage jihad against it. Begin with your soul and wage a military campaign against it.\u201d Source: Muh\u0323a\u0304sabat al-Nafs\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7983,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/12\/masjid-learning-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":35538,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Entering mosque to learn is jihad in the way of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever enters our mosque to teach goodness, or to learn it himself, is like one waging jihad in the way of Allah. Whoever enters it for another reason, he is an observer of what does not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18222,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/20\/seeking-knowledge-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":35538,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Seeking knowledge is jihad in way of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever goes out seeking knowledge is in the way of Allah until he returns.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2647 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11356,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/15\/lesser-greater-jihad-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":35538,"position":5},"title":"Ibrahim on Jihad: Greater Jihad is struggle to purify the heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Ibrahim ibn Abi 'Alqamah, may Allah have mercy on him, said to his people when they returned from a military expedition, \u201cYou have come from the lesser jihad, but you have not performed the greater jihad.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat is the greater jihad?\u201d Ibrahim said, \u201cIt is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u064